+
+Data loss happens fast. A MacBook spill during load shedding, a failed iMac drive after a power surge, an iPad that won't restart after a fall, these are the situations we handle daily here at our Hyde Park workshop. In Johannesburg, where load shedding has become part of life, power-related data loss has increased noticeably. The question clients ask most often isn't "Can you recover my data?" but "How much will it cost?"
