+
+If the device has already been powered on after water exposure, corrosion may have progressed to the storage controller. This makes recovery harder and more expensive. Our advice: don't turn the device on. Don't let it dry naturally. Bring it to us immediately.
+
+We've recovered data from more than 12,000 water-damaged devices. Most are recoverable if brought in before secondary damage occurs.
+
+## Our Warranty on Recovery Work
+
+Every data recovery at ZA Support includes a 3-year warranty on the recovered drive or storage module we install. If the replacement component fails within 36 months, we replace it at no charge. This isn't standard in Johannesburg, many recovery services offer none.
+
+We also verify recovered data before returning your device. You'll see a full file listing and spot-check several folders before you leave our Hyde Park workshop. If data is missing or corrupted, we know before you do and can attempt additional extraction if possible.
+
